ckists&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n		&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div id=&quot;content&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;div class=&quot;banner&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;http://www.asquithlondon.com/image/data/banners/homepage%20ctas/COMMUNITY.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;h1&gt;\r\n		Our Ethics&lt;/h1&gt;\r\n	&lt;div&gt;\r\n		Asquith London manufactures our clothing in a family run factory, established in 1994, based in Denizli in sunny Southern Turkey.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;div&gt;\r\n		&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;div&gt;\r\n		The employees in the factory receive overtime pay, food support and comfortable working conditions and regular holidays. They work in a clean, safe environment, and the youngest person working in the factory is 19 years old. The factory receives regular audits to ensure they have high standards. We do not believe in child labour and poor working conditions.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;div&gt;\r\n		&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;div&gt;\r\n		The factory is an organic factory, and we use organic dyes. The organic cotton fabrics are GOTS certified (Global Organic Textile standard)&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;div&gt;\r\n		&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;div&gt;\r\n		We use Bamboo and Organic Cotton fabrics for our clothing. Ethical, sustainable, breathable, comfortable, natural. Read more about our fabrics.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;div&gt;\r\n		&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;div&gt;\r\n		&lt;strong&gt;OUR PACKAGING&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;div&gt;\r\n		Where possible we try not to create waste; our postcards and marketing materials, labels and packaging materials are recycled.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;div&gt;\r\n		&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;div&gt;\r\n		&lt;strong&gt;OUR PHILOSOPHY &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;div&gt;\r\n		We aim to listen to our customers; we love your feedback, we’ve designed styles for you, fabrics for you.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;div&gt;\r\n		We strive to provide quality garments that you can enjoy season after season. We are the opposite of ‘fast disposable fashion’. The Asquith range is designed for yoga and Pilates, but also to work with your daily lifestyle.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;div&gt;\r\n		 &lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;div&gt;\r\n		I design the range for you. I am inspired by my own yoga practice, my teachers, my lifestyle and requirements and the requirements of all the women I meet who work, play and live a full and busy life.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;div&gt;\r\n		&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;div&gt;\r\n		Asquith London is comprised of a friendly team of people. We believe in excellent customer service, strong communication, openness and honesty in all things.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;div&gt;\r\n		&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;div&gt;\r\n		We love to hear from you with any thoughts or feedback you may have.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;div&gt;\r\n		&lt;a href=&quot;mailto:alice@asquithlondon.com&quot;&gt;alice@asquithlondon.com&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;div&gt;\r\n		Alice Asquith&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;div&gt;\r\n		Managing Director&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;div&gt;\r\n		Asquith London&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n'),(15,1,'Our Style','&lt;div id=&quot;column-left&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;div class=&quot;box&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;div class=&quot;box-heading&quot;&gt;\r\n			&lt;a href=&quot;index.php?route=information/information&amp;amp;information_id=4&quot;&gt;About Us&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n		&lt;div class=&quot;box-content&quot;&gt;\r\n			&lt;p&gt;\r\n				&lt;a href=&quot;index.php?route=information/information&amp;amp;information_id=13&quot;&gt;Our Ethics&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n			&lt;p&gt;\r\n				&lt;a href=&quot;index.php?route=information/information&amp;amp;information_id=14&quot;&gt;Our Fabrics&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n			&lt;p&gt;\r\n				&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;index.php?route=information/information&amp;amp;information_id=15&quot;&gt;Our Style&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n			&lt;p&gt;\r\n				&lt;a href=&quot;index.php?route=information/information&amp;amp;information_id=16&quot;&gt;Meet Alice&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n			&lt;p&gt;\r\n				&lt;a href=&quot;index.php?route=news/ncategory&amp;amp;ncat=60&quot;&gt;In The Press&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n			&lt;p&gt;\r\n				&lt;a href=&quot;index.php?route=information/information&amp;amp;information_id=11&quot;&gt;Stockists&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n		&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div id=&quot;content&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;div class=&quot;banner&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;http://daffodill.totallyboundless.com/image/data/OUR-STYLE.jpg&quot; style=&quot;width: 757px; height: 214px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;h1&gt;\r\n		Our Style&lt;/h1&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;I wear Asquith clothes all the time and everywhere: at home, for my work (as a yoga teacher). And bamboo leggings with ankle boots are gorgeous when going out! I also get extra hugs from my colleagues thanks to the super soft material. Maya&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		We see today\'s woman as healthy and active, she cares for the environment, leads a full life, wants to look good and be comfortable.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		Asquith London offers 2 collections per year, but we always try to keep our \'bestsellers\' in stock and roll these styles on, season after season, due to their popularity.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		The Asquith range includes signature styles that can be layered and worn in different ways to suit your shape and lifestyle, in highest quality materials that feel smooth and soft against the skin; breathable, chemical free fabrics; brushed certified organic cotton and drapey bamboo jersey with a delicate Swarovski crystal signature. Quality pieces, that won’t shrink, fade, bobble or stretch.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n		Asquith London - for yoga, Pilates and living in.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		Asquith London offers the perfect selection of organic cotton and bamboo clothes designed specifically for your yoga (and Pilates) practice. The Asquith London collection contains yoga clothes in coordinating pieces in contrasting soft tones with flattering styling so you can create your own individual ‘look’.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		And in natural breathable and organic fabric for comfortable and easy freedom of movement, and firm built-in support, our yoga clothing styles ensure pure comfort at all times, leaving the wearer to focus on her yoga or Pilates practice.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		Asquith London ensures a luxurious feeling against your skin, as if it were a second skin. Each garment too has been very specifically designed to ensure:&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		- Pure comfort – no tight elastic bands dig into the hips or waist giving one complete freedom of movement&lt;br /&gt;\r\n		- 100% Support – the designs along with the weight of the fabric and the percentage of Elastane in the fabric ensure one has no need to wear a bra&lt;br /&gt;\r\n		- Versatility – One could wear our range at yoga, Pilates, gym, as well as for spa and leisure wear&lt;br /&gt;\r\n		- Timelessness – the designs will never be out of fashion – they are elegant and classic&lt;br /&gt;\r\n		- Ageless – the range is designed for anyone aged 30’s – 60’s…&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		&lt;br /&gt;\r\n		&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n'),(16,1,'Meet Alice','&lt;div id=&quot;column-left&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;div class=&quot;box&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;div class=&quot;box-heading&quot;&gt;\r\n			&lt;a href=&quot;index.php?route=information/information&amp;amp;information_id=4&quot;&gt;About Us&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n		&lt;div class=&quot;box-content&quot;&gt;\r\n			&lt;p&gt;\r\n				&lt;a href=&quot;index.php?route=information/information&amp;amp;information_id=13&quot;&gt;Our Ethics&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n			&lt;p&gt;\r\n				&lt;a href=&quot;index.php?route=information/information&amp;amp;information_id=14&quot;&gt;Our Fabrics&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n			&lt;p&gt;\r\n				&lt;a href=&quot;index.php?route=information/information&amp;amp;information_id=15&quot;&gt;Our Style&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n			&lt;p&gt;\r\n				&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;index.php?route=information/information&amp;amp;information_id=16&quot;&gt;Meet Alice&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n			&lt;p&gt;\r\n				&lt;a href=&quot;index.php?route=news/ncategory&amp;amp;ncat=60&quot;&gt;In The Press&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n			&lt;p&gt;\r\n				&lt;a href=&quot;index.php?route=information/information&amp;amp;information_id=11&quot;&gt;Stockists&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n		&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div id=&quot;content&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;div class=&quot;banner&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;http://www.asquithlondon.com/image/data/banners/homepage%20ctas/COMMUNITY.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;h1&gt;\r\n		Meet Alice&lt;/h1&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;div&gt;\r\n		&lt;p&gt;\r\n			&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;http://daffodill.totallyboundless.com/image/data/aa-portrait-oct%2007%20%283%29.jpg&quot; style=&quot;width: 380px; height: 570px; float: left;&quot; /&gt;Descended from a long line of creative women, Alice was very much a part of this passion for design, sewing, and beautiful quality fabrics since early childhood – influenced by her mother, grandmother and great-grandmother – who made and designed their own beautiful clothes.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n		&lt;p&gt;\r\n			Asquith London was born out of Alice’s desire for natural, elegant clothing in flattering styles, which Alice felt just weren’t available in a yoga/leisurewear brand. The Asquith London range today provides the ultimate ethical lifestyle&lt;/p&gt;\r\n		&lt;p&gt;\r\n			solution, offering classic, versatile cotton and bamboo jersey pieces for today’s woman’s busy lifestyle - for yoga, Pilates, for running around town, meeting friends, travel, holidays or relaxing at home. Quality pieces, designed for complete comfort and total freedom of movement, that won’t shrink, fade, bobble or stretch.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n		&lt;p&gt;\r\n			Believing clothing trends, gimmicks or logos should never overpower the women wearing the clothes, the Asquith label&amp;nbsp;focuses on soft jersey layering in flattering shapes and comfortable styles – offering a range that is feminine and elegant, and not ‘sporty’ in feel. All the collections are designed by Alice Asquith and carry a delicate Swarovski crystal signature.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n		&lt;p&gt;\r\n			The pieces can be mixed and matched with existing wardrobe items giving women creative freedom and individual style.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n		&lt;p&gt;\r\n			The Asquith London brand is a British, designer brand which stands alone in its styling and exceptional quality. Asquith London is deeply committed to each and every person who purchases our pieces, the intention being that whilst wearing our wear, you are able to access your peaceful energy without any constraints and restrictions.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n		&lt;p&gt;\r\n			&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;div&gt;\r\n		&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;div&gt;\r\n		&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n'),(4,1,'About Us','&lt;div id=&quot;column-left&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;div class=&quot;box&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;div class=&quot;box-heading&quot;&gt;\r\n			&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;index.php?route=information/information&amp;amp;information_id=4&quot;&gt;About Us&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n		&lt;div class=&quot;box-content&quot;&gt;\r\n			&lt;p&gt;\r\n				&lt;a href=&quot;index.php?route=information/information&amp;amp;information_id=13&quot;&gt;Our Ethics&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n			&lt;p&gt;\r\n				&lt;a href=&quot;index.php?route=information/information&amp;amp;information_id=14&quot;&gt;Our Fabrics&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n			&lt;p&gt;\r\n				&lt;a href=&quot;index.php?route=information/information&amp;amp;information_id=15&quot;&gt;Our Style&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n			&lt;p&gt;\r\n				&lt;a href=&quot;index.php?route=information/information&amp;amp;information_id=16&quot;&gt;Meet Alice&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n			&lt;p&gt;\r\n				&lt;a href=&quot;index.php?route=news/ncategory&amp;amp;ncat=60&quot;&gt;In The Press&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n			&lt;p&gt;\r\n				&lt;a href=&quot;index.php?route=information/information&amp;amp;information_id=11&quot;&gt;Stockists&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n		&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div id=&quot;content&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;div class=&quot;banner&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;http://www.asquithlondon.com/image/data/banners/homepage%20ctas/CONTACT-US.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;h1&gt;\r\n		About Us&lt;/h1&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		Asquith London manufactures our clothing in a family run factory, established in 1994, based in Denizli in sunny Southern Turkey.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		The employees in the factory receive overtime pay, food support and comfortable working conditions and regular holidays. They work in a clean, safe environment, and the youngest person working in the factory is 19 years old. The factory receives regular audits to ensure they have high standards. We do not believe in child labour and poor working conditions.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		The factory is an organic factory, and we use organic dyes. The organic cotton fabrics are GOTS certified (Global Organic Textile standard)&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		We use Bamboo and Organic Cotton fabrics for our clothing. Ethical, sustainable, breathable, comfortable, natural. Read more about our fabrics.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		&lt;strong&gt;OUR PACKAGING&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		Where possible we try not to create waste; our postcards and marketing materials, labels and packaging materials are recycled.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		&lt;strong&gt;OUR PHILOSOPHY&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		We aim to listen to our customers; we love your feedback, we’ve designed styles for you, fabrics for you.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		We strive to provide quality garments that you can enjoy season after season. We are the opposite of ‘fast disposable fashion’. The Asquith range is designed for yoga and Pilates, but also to work with your daily lifestyle.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		 I design the range for you. I am inspired by my own yoga practice, my teachers, my lifestyle and requirements and the requirements of all the women I meet who work, play and live a full and busy life.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		Asquith London is comprised of a friendly team of people. We believe in excellent customer service, strong communication, openness and honesty in all things.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		We love to hear from you with any thoughts or feedback you may have.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		&lt;a href=&quot;mailto:alice@asquithlondon.com&quot;&gt;alice@asquithlondon.com&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		Alice Asquith&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		Managing Director&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		Asquith London&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n'),(17,1,'Brochure','&lt;div id=&quot;column-left&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;div class=&quot;box&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;div class=&quot;box-heading&quot;&gt;\r\n			&lt;a href=&quot;index.php?route=information/information&amp;amp;information_id=25&quot;&gt;Contact Us&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n		&lt;div class=&quot;box-content&quot;&gt;\r\n			&lt;div class=&quot;box-category&quot;&gt;\r\n				&lt;ul&gt;\r\n					&lt;li&gt;\r\n						&lt;a href=&quot;index.php?route=information/information&amp;amp;information_id=25&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Our Contact Details&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n					&lt;li&gt;\r\n						&lt;a href=&quot;index.php?route=information/information&amp;amp;information_id=13&q