&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 18px; font-family: Arial;&quot;&gt;Asquith London&lt;br /&gt;\r\n		7 Leamington Road Villas&lt;br /&gt;\r\n		London&lt;br /&gt;\r\n		W11 1HS&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 18px; font-family: Arial;&quot;&gt;VAT number - 777 9312 80&lt;br /&gt;\r\n		Asquith Ltd is a limited company Registered in England.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n		Registered Office Address - Hazlems Fenton, Palladium House, 1-4 Argyll Street, London W1F 7LD&lt;br /&gt;\r\n		Company Registration number – 4110730&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n'),(12,1,'Wholesale Enquiries','&lt;div id=&quot;column-left&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;div class=&quot;box&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;div class=&quot;box-heading&quot;&gt;\r\n			&lt;a href=&quot;index.php?route=information/information&amp;amp;information_id=10&quot;&gt;Contact Us&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n		&lt;div class=&quot;box-content&quot;&gt;\r\n			&lt;p&gt;\r\n				&lt;a href=&quot;index.php?route=information/information&amp;amp;information_id=10&quot;&gt;Our Contact Details&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n			&lt;p&gt;\r\n				&lt;a href=&quot;index.php?route=information/information&amp;amp;information_id=11&quot;&gt;Stockists&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n			&lt;p&gt;\r\n				&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;index.php?route=information/information&amp;amp;information_id=12&quot;&gt;Wholesale Enquiries&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n		&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div id=&quot;content&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;div class=&quot;banner&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;http://www.asquithlondon.com/image/data/banners/homepage%20ctas/CONTACT-US.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;h1&gt;\r\n		Wholesale Enquiries&lt;/h1&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		Asquith London sells in boutiques, yoga studios, Pilates studios, luxury spas and hotels around the world.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		Asquith London will be exhibiting at the following forthcoming Trade &amp;amp; Consumer shows:-&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		The Yoga Show at Olympia, 26th – 28th October 2012&lt;br /&gt;\r\n		Pure London at Olympia, 10th – 12th February 2013&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		If you would like information about the Asquith London collection please contact us on:-&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		&lt;a href=&quot;mailto:contact@asquithlondon.com&quot;&gt;contact@asquithlondon.com&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n'),(19,1,'Delivery &amp; Postage','&lt;div id=&quot;column-left&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;div class=&quot;box&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;div class=&quot;box-heading&quot;&gt;\r\n			&lt;a href=&quot;index.php?route=information/information&amp;amp;information_id=18&quot;&gt;Customer Service&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n		&lt;div class=&quot;box-content&quot;&gt;\r\n			&lt;p&gt;\r\n				&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;index.php?route=information/information&amp;amp;information_id=19&quot;&gt;Delivery &amp;amp; Postage&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n			&lt;p&gt;\r\n				&lt;a href=&quot;index.php?route=information/information&amp;amp;information_id=20&quot;&gt;Refunds &amp;amp; Exchanges&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n			&lt;p&gt;\r\n				&lt;a href=&quot;index.php?route=information/information&amp;amp;information_id=21&quot;&gt;Sizing&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n			&lt;p&gt;\r\n				&lt;a href=&quot;index.php?route=account/voucher&quot;&gt;Gift Vouchers&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n			&lt;p&gt;\r\n				&lt;a href=&quot;index.php?route=product/category&amp;amp;path=73&quot;&gt;Clearance&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n			&lt;p&gt;\r\n				&lt;a href=&quot;index.php?route=information/information&amp;amp;information_id=5&quot;&gt;Terms &amp;amp; Conditions&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n			&lt;p&gt;\r\n				&lt;a href=&quot;index.php?route=information/information&amp;amp;information_id=23&quot;&gt;Security &amp;amp; Privacy&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n		&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div id=&quot;content&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;div class=&quot;banner&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;http://www.asquithlondon.com/image/data/banners/homepage%20ctas/CUSTOMER-SERVICE.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;h1&gt;\r\n		Delivery&amp;nbsp;&amp;amp; Postage&lt;/h1&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		We aim to dispatch standard delivery orders within 24 hours of receiving your order (unless it’s a weekend); however, dispatch can be subject to availability and could take up to 2 working days during busy periods, therefore please allow 3-5 working days for delivery.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(255, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;DURING THE CHRISTMAS PERIOD, PLEASE ALLOW A FEW MORE DAYS FOR YOUR ORDER TO ARRIVE, AS ROYAL MAIL MAY TAKE LONGER TO DELIVER&amp;nbsp;- IF YOU REQUIRE YOUR ORDER URGENTLY, PLEASE CHOOSE THE &lt;u&gt;NEXT DAY DELIVERY&lt;/u&gt;&amp;nbsp; OPTION&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		You will receive an e-mail confirmation of receipt of your order. Please keep this on file for your records.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		All parcels for UK addresses require a signature on delivery.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		We send orders via the Royal Mail on a Recorded delivery/Signed For service which is a more secure method and requires a signature on delivery. If you are not in to receive the parcel, the postman will leave a card and you can collect the parcel from your local post office.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		PLEASE NOTE - there is a section on your order form where you can write delivery instructions for the postman - ie if you\'re out where you\'d like the parcel left, which we will then write on your parcel for the attention of the postman. Please note, we are NOT responsible for items left/delivered by the postman.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		&lt;strong&gt;Delivery Charges&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		UK Mainland - £4.95&lt;br /&gt;\r\n		UK Next Day Delivery - £6.95&lt;br /&gt;\r\n		UK - Ireland, Channel Islands &amp;amp; Jersey - £7.95&lt;br /&gt;\r\n		Within the EU - £9.00 (Please allow 5 - 7 working day for delivery)&lt;br /&gt;\r\n		Rest of the World - £12.00 (Please allow 7 - 9 working days for delivery)&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		&lt;strong&gt;Next Day Delivery&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		Your order must be placed by 11am on a weekday for UK next day delivery.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		&lt;strong&gt;International Orders&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		International orders are sent using the Royal Mail International Signed For service and can take up to 7-14 working days to be delivered. This is a more secure method and requires a signature on delivery. If you are not in to receive the parcel, the postman will leave a card and you can collect the parcel from your local post office. Larger parcels are sent by Interlink or UPS for Canada, USA orders, whichever the warehouse feels is the safest, fastest method of delivery for your order.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		Please note that Asquith London is unable to calculate local customs and sales tax with all international deliveries. You will be notified by your local customs authority once your order has reached your country. They will accurately calculate the total amount of customs and sales tax which is to be paid before you may receive your goods.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n		Please contact us, at &lt;a href=&quot;mailto:contact@asquithlondon.com&quot;&gt;contact@asquithlondon.com&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;if you do have any further questions.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		&lt;strong&gt;Payment&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		We accept the following credit and debit cards:&lt;br /&gt;\r\n		Visa, Mastercard, Maestro, Switch, Solo, Visa Debit and Paypal&lt;br /&gt;\r\n		This service is secure, however if you would rather pay over the phone, you can call us on (0)207 792 9414 to make your order.&amp;nbsp; When using a credit card to pay online or on the phone you will need to be the cardholder and give the registered cardholder’s address and other details required by us to verify the transaction. For security reasons we do not keep your card details on file.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		&lt;strong&gt;Availability of Items&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		We try to keep our website up to date at all times showing available stock. Sometimes items sell out very fast, when this occurs we will let you know - to either offer you an alternative or advise when the item will next be in stock. We will aim to deliver the requested goods as soon as possible and update you as to timescale.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n'),(20,1,'Refunds and Exchanges','&lt;div id=&quot;column-left&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;div class=&quot;box&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;div class=&quot;box-heading&quot;&gt;\r\n			&lt;a href=&quot;index.php?route=information/information&amp;amp;information_id=18&quot;&gt;Customer Service&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n		&lt;div class=&quot;box-content&quot;&gt;\r\n			&lt;p&gt;\r\n				&lt;a href=&quot;index.php?route=information/information&amp;amp;information_id=19&quot;&gt;Delivery &amp;amp; Postage&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n			&lt;p&gt;\r\n				&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;index.php?route=information/information&amp;amp;information_id=20&quot;&gt;Refunds &amp;amp; Exchanges&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n			&lt;p&gt;\r\n				&lt;a href=&quot;index.php?route=information/information&amp;amp;information_id=21&quot;&gt;Sizing&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n			&lt;p&gt;\r\n				&lt;a href=&quot;index.php?route=account/voucher&quot;&gt;Gift Vouchers&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n			&lt;p&gt;\r\n				&lt;a href=&quot;index.php?route=product/category&amp;amp;path=73&quot;&gt;Clearance&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n			&lt;p&gt;\r\n				&lt;a href=&quot;index.php?route=information/information&amp;amp;information_id=5&quot;&gt;Terms &amp;amp; Conditions&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n			&lt;p&gt;\r\n				&lt;a href=&quot;index.php?route=information/information&amp;amp;information_id=23&quot;&gt;Security &amp;amp; Privacy&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n		&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div id=&quot;content&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;div class=&quot;banner&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;http://www.asquithlondon.com/image/data/banners/homepage%20ctas/CUSTOMER-SERVICE.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;h1&gt;\r\n		Refunds and Exchanges&lt;/h1&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 18px; font-family: Arial;&quot;&gt;If you are not perfectly happy with a product we will be delighted to offer you a refund or an exchange as long as the products are returned within 14 days&amp;nbsp; in perfect condition, unworn, and in their original packaging.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		&lt;u&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 18px; font-family: Arial;&quot;&gt;For the Christmas period we have extended our returns policy. All returns need to be sent back to us by the 9th January 2013. The items need to be in perfect condition, unworn and in their original packaging for us to be able to offer an exchange or refund. We can only process a refund onto the original credit / debit card that was used to place the order.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 18px; font-family: Arial;&quot;&gt;Please be careful when trying on Tops that you do not leave lipstick or deodorant marks.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 18px; font-family: Arial;&quot;&gt;Please note that we want you to be happy with your Asquith London choice, therefore we do also accept exchanges &amp;amp; offer refunds on SALE ITEMS as long as the items are returned in perfect condition, unworn, and in their original packaging.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 18px; font-family: Arial;&quot;&gt;And it’s always helpful to know why you’d like to exchange your item – because we always aim to offer the best possible service and want to improve the styles for you – therefore your feedback is always invaluable to us.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 18px; font-family: Arial;&quot;&gt;We are always very happy to help you choose something else, therefore if you would like advice on alternative styles or sizing please email &lt;a href=&quot;mailto:contact@asquithlondon.com&quot;&gt;contact@asquithlondon.com&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 18px; font-family: Arial;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;How to Return or Exchange an Order&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 18px; font-family: Arial;&quot;&gt;Please complete the Returns form sent out with your order. Please list the contents of the package, your name, the reason for returning the product, and whether you would like an exchange or refund.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 18px; font-family: Arial;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Please then pack up the item carefully and return to the following address:-&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 18px; font-family: Arial;&quot;&gt;ASQUITH LONDON&lt;br /&gt;\r\n		c/o Kathy Valentine&lt;br /&gt;\r\n		Phoenix International Freight Services Ltd&lt;br /&gt;\r\n		International House&lt;br /&gt;\r\n		Hodgeson Way&lt;br /&gt;\r\n		Wickford&lt;br /&gt;\r\n		Essex&lt;br /&gt;\r\n		SS11 8YB&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 18px; font-family: Arial;&quot;&gt;When returning your parcel, to ensure that it reaches us safely, we strongly recommend that you send the parcel to us via recorded or special delivery and keep the recorded or special delivery receipt from your local Post Office for your records. Please keep this receipt safe, as, in the unlikely event of the parcel going missing, this is your proof of postage. Please note that we are not responsible for goods lost in transit and cannot refund without the returned items.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 18px; font-family: Arial;&quot;&gt;Please note that there is no cost to exchange an item, we will cover the postage for the exchange item to be sent to you.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 18px; font-family: Arial;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Faulty Items&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 18px; font-family: Arial;&quot;&gt;In the unlikely event that your goods are damaged or faulty you are of course entitled to a full refund / replacement, including the cost of returning the item back to our warehouse. Please email us on &lt;a href=&quot;mailto:contact@asquithlondon.com&quot;&gt;contact@asquithlondon.com&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;and let us know the reason for the garment being faulty then we can resolve the situation in the best way possible.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 18px; font-family: Arial;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Again, please ensure the item is returned within 14 days.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n'),(21,1,'Sizing','&lt;div id=&quot;column-left&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;div class=&quot;box&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;div class=&quot;box-heading&quot;&gt;\r\n			&lt;a href=&quot;index.php?route=information/information&amp;amp;information_id=18&quot;&gt;Customer Service&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n		&lt;div class=&quot;box-content&quot;&gt;\r\n			&lt;p&gt;\r\n				&lt;a href=&quot;index.php?route=information/information&amp;amp;information_id=19&quot;&gt;Delivery &amp;amp; Postage&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n			&lt;p&gt;\r\n				&lt;a href=&quot;index.php?route=information/information&amp;amp;information_id=20&quot;&gt;Refunds &amp;amp; Exchanges&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n			&lt;p&gt;\r\n				&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;index.php?route=information/information&amp;amp;information_id=21&quot;&gt;Sizing&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n			&lt;p&gt;\r\n				&lt;a href=&quot;index.php?route=account/voucher&quot;&gt;Gift Vouchers&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n			&lt;p&gt;\r\n				&lt;a href=&quot;index.php?route=product/category&amp;amp;path=73&quot;&gt;Clearance&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n			&lt;p&gt;\r\n				&lt;a href=&quot;index.php?route=information/information&amp;amp;information_id=5&quot;&gt;Terms &amp;amp; Conditions&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n			&lt;p&gt;\r\n				&lt;a href=&quot;index.php?route=information/information&amp;amp;information_id=23&quot;&gt;Security &amp;amp; Privacy&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n		&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div id=&quot;content&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;div class=&quot;banner&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;http://www.asquithlondon.com/image/data/banners/homepage%20ctas/CUSTOMER-SERVICE.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;h1&gt;\r\n		Sizing&lt;/h1&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		&lt;b&gt;Measurement Guide&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		Measure your bust, waist and hip and compare your measurements with our size guide to help you determine what size to buy.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;ol&gt;\r\n		&lt;li&gt;\r\n			Bust - take the measurement across fullest part of your bust and across your shoulder blades.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n		&lt;li&gt;\r\n			Waist - measure around your natural waistline.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n		&lt;li&gt;\r\n			Hips - measure at the widest part.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n		&lt;li&gt;\r\n			Inside leg - measure from the top of the inside leg at the crutch to the anklebone.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		Items may vary in size from the guide depending on the style and fabric but they will still fit the body size indicated.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		Please note that in the table below, all measurements are body measurements and not garment measurements. If you have any questions regarding sizing please don’t hesitate to contact us at contact@asquithlondon.com&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;table border=&quot;1&quot; style=&quot;width: 100%;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;tbody&gt;\r\n			&lt;tr&gt;\r\n				&lt;td style=&quot;width: 126px; &quot;&gt;\r\n					&lt;p&gt;\r\n						&lt;strong&gt;SIZING&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n					&lt;p&gt;\r\n						UK&lt;br /&gt;\r\n						EURO&lt;br /&gt;\r\n						USA&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;/td&gt;\r\n				&lt;td colspan=&quot;2&quot;&gt;\r\n					&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;\r\n						XS&lt;/p&gt;\r\n					&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;\r\n						8&lt;br /&gt;\r\n						36&lt;br /&gt;\r\n						4&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;/td&gt;\r\n				&lt;td colspan=&quot;2&quot;&gt;\r\n					&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;\r\n						S&lt;/p&gt;\r\n					&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;\r\n						10&lt;br /&gt;\r\n						38&lt;br /&gt;\r\n						6&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;/td&gt;\r\n				&lt;td colspan=&quot;2&quot;&gt;\r\n					&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;\r\n						M&lt;/p&gt;\r\n					&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;\r\n						12&lt;br /&gt;\r\n						40&lt;br /&gt;\r\n						8&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;/td&gt;\r\n				&lt;td colspan=&quot;2&quot;&gt;\r\n					&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;\r\n						L&lt;/p&gt;\r\n					&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;\r\n						14&lt;br /&gt;\r\n						42&lt;br /&gt;\r\n						10&lt;/p&gt;\r\