tion/information&amp;information_id=30&quot;&gt;Affiliates&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n        \r\n        &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://plus.google.com/102388213141542496784/posts&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Google Plus&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n        &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.facebook.com/pages/Asquith-London-Organic-Cotton-Bamboo-Lifestyle-and-Yoga-Clothing/170293469708750?sk=wall&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Facebook&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n        &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://twitter.com/AsquithLondon&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Twitter&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n        &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://pinterest.com/asquithlondon/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&quot;&gt;Pinterest&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n		&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div id=&quot;content&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;div class=&quot;banner&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;http://www.asquithlondon.com/image/data/banners/homepage%20ctas/COMMUNITY.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;h1&gt;\r\n		Affiliates - Friends of Asquith London&lt;/h1&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;http://www.asquithlondon.com/image/data/A5-Leaflet1---FRONT-LOW-RES-JPEG.jpg&quot; style=&quot;width: 400px; height: 567px; border-width: 0px; border-style: solid; margin: 6px; float: left; &quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		Join Asquith London\'s affliliate scheme - Friends of Asquith London.&amp;nbsp;A risk free way for you to earn money promoting Asquith\'s yoga clothing and share in&amp;nbsp;our continued success.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		If you have your own website and email database then you’re eligible to become a Friend of Asquith London and earn money by recommending your favourite, quality, ethical yoga and Pilates clothing brand.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;div&gt;\r\n		&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;div&gt;\r\n		&lt;strong&gt;As a Friend of Asquith London you’ll receive:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;ul&gt;\r\n		&lt;li&gt;\r\n			An exclusive discount code that entitles your friends &amp;amp; students to 15% off&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n		&lt;li&gt;\r\n			Flyers with your exclusive discount code – to hand out to students&lt;/li&gt;\r\n		&lt;li&gt;\r\n			15% of all sales (less postage) using your exclusive code (to be paid monthly&amp;nbsp;into your bank account)&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n		&lt;li&gt;\r\n			2 complimentary items of Asquith London, following your first promotional&amp;nbsp;email to your database&lt;/li&gt;\r\n		&lt;li&gt;\r\n			A special 30% off teacher discount for you, so that you can buy Asquith&amp;nbsp;clothing at 30% off….whenever you want! (Please note that promotional codes do not work on sale items)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;div&gt;\r\n		&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;div&gt;\r\n		&lt;strong&gt;As a Friend of Asquith London you agree to:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;ul&gt;\r\n		&lt;li&gt;\r\n			Promote and link to Asquith London via your website&lt;/li&gt;\r\n		&lt;li&gt;\r\n			Send a minimum of 4 emails/yr promoting Asquith London to your database&lt;/li&gt;\r\n		&lt;li&gt;\r\n			Introduce and promote Asquith London in your classes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n		&lt;li&gt;\r\n			Review your complimentary pieces as www.asquithlondon.com&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;div&gt;\r\n		&lt;a href=&quot;mailto:katherine@k-a-s.co.uk?subject=Friends%20of%20Asquith%20London&quot;&gt;Email Katherine&lt;/a&gt; for more information and to request an application form.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n'),(31,1,'Our Store','&lt;table border=&quot;0&quot; style=&quot;width: 1080px;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;tbody&gt;\r\n		&lt;tr&gt;\r\n			&lt;td&gt;\r\n				&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;http://www.thepapillonshop.co.uk/image/data/Our%20Store/010712-STORE-01.jpg&quot; style=&quot;float: left; width: 716px; height: 537px; &quot; /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td style=&quot;align:top;&quot;&gt;\r\n				&lt;h2&gt;\r\n					Our Store&lt;/h2&gt;\r\n				&lt;p&gt;\r\n					It all started in the heart of the Brighton Laines. Nestled in the jewellery quarter Papillon was born.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p&gt;\r\n					When the shop moved into a larger space it was able to grow into one of Brightons best loved interior boutiques.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p&gt;\r\n					We have a team of staff all passionate about creating harmonious settings and original rooms within the home who are available to provide advice, ideas and thoughts on how to get the most from your home.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p&gt;\r\n					If you’re ever in Brighton then do pop in for a browse, chat, shopping spree or all three!&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;br /&gt;\r\n				Address:&lt;br /&gt;\r\n				Papillon&lt;br /&gt;\r\n				8 Union Street&lt;br /&gt;\r\n				Brighton&lt;br /&gt;\r\n				BN1 1HA&lt;br /&gt;\r\n				&lt;br /&gt;\r\n				Opening Hours:&lt;br /&gt;\r\n				Mon - Sat 10am - 6pm&lt;br /&gt;\r\n				Sunday 11am - 5pm&lt;br /&gt;\r\n				&lt;br /&gt;\r\n				Telephone:&lt;br /&gt;\r\n				01273 720 333&lt;/td&gt;\r\n		&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n	&lt;/tbody&gt;\r\n&lt;/table&gt;\r\n&lt;table border=&quot;0&quot; style=&quot;width: 1080px;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;tbody&gt;\r\n		&lt;tr&gt;\r\n			&lt;td&gt;\r\n				&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;http://www.thepapillonshop.co.uk/image/data/Our%20Store/010712-STORE-02.jpg&quot; style=&quot;float: left; width: 355px; height: 237px; &quot; /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td&gt;\r\n				&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;http://www.thepapillonshop.co.uk/image/data/Our%20Store/010712-STORE-03.jpg&quot; style=&quot;float: left; width: 355px; height: 237px; &quot; /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td&gt;\r\n				&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;http://www.thepapillonshop.co.uk/image/data/Our%20Store/010712-STORE-04.jpg&quot; style=&quot;float: left; width: 355px; height: 237px; &quot; /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;\r\n		&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n	&lt;/tbody&gt;\r\n&lt;/table&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n'),(32,1