idth: 355px; height: 473px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td&gt;\r\n				&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;http://www.thepapillonshop.co.uk/image/data/content%20pages/About%20Us/300612-ANDREW-MARTIN-ABOUT-03.jpg&quot; style=&quot;width: 355px; height: 473px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;\r\n		&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n	&lt;/tbody&gt;\r\n&lt;/table&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n'),(33,1,'Delivery &amp; Returns','&lt;table border=&quot;0&quot; style=&quot;width: 1080px;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;tbody&gt;\r\n		&lt;tr&gt;\r\n			&lt;td style=&quot;width:600px&quot;&gt;\r\n				&lt;h2&gt;\r\n					Delivery Infromation&lt;/h2&gt;\r\n				&lt;p&gt;\r\n					At Papillon we aim to deliver an efficient service from when we first receive your order.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p&gt;\r\n					All goods are sent via &lt;strong&gt;Interlink Express&lt;/strong&gt; who acts as our main Courier. (Please note that another courier may, at our discretion deliver certain items that are bulky such as furniture.)&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p&gt;\r\n					To ensure that you are kept up to date with your delivery time please ensure you give us an email address, Interlink Express will send a confirmation email regarding the hour of your delivery.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p&gt;\r\n					All orders recived will be on next day delivery for UK Mainland.(excludes weekends)&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p&gt;\r\n					If an item is sent to an address that you specified when you placed the order and it turns out to be incorrect then we are not liable if this item does not reach you.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p&gt;\r\n					International Orders are welcome and special arrangments can be made by calling us on 01273 720333.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p&gt;\r\n					thepapillonshop.com is not liable for delays that are incurred via transit by Interlink Express&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p&gt;\r\n					Any orders placed over the weekend or during a Bank Holiday will be dealt with on the next working day.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p&gt;\r\n					Below details our standard delivery charges...&lt;/p&gt;\r\n			&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td&gt;\r\n				&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;http://www.thepapillonshop.co.uk/image/data/content%20pages/300612-DELIVERY.jpg&quot; style=&quot;width: 418px; height: 361px; float: right;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;\r\n		&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n	&lt;/tbody&gt;\r\n&lt;/table&gt;\r\n&lt;table border=&quot;0&quot; style=&quot;width: 1080px;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;tbody&gt;\r\n		&lt;tr&gt;\r\n			&lt;td&gt;\r\n				&lt;h2&gt;\r\n					UK Mainland &amp;amp; Northern Ireland&lt;/h2&gt;\r\n			&lt;/td&gt;\r\n		&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n		&lt;tr&gt;\r\n			&lt;td style=&quot;width: 300px;&quot;&gt;\r\n				Home Accessories &amp;amp; Fragrances etc.&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td&gt;\r\n				£6.95 Interlink Delivery Service&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td style=&quot;width:300px&quot;&gt;\r\n				&amp;nbsp;&lt;/td&gt;\r\n		&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n		&lt;tr&gt;\r\n			&lt;td style=&quot;width:300px&quot;&gt;\r\n				Cards &amp;amp; Other Small Items&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td&gt;\r\n				£1.50 Royal Mail Delivery Service&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td style=&quot;width:300px&quot;&gt;\r\n				&amp;nbsp;&lt;/td&gt;\r\n		&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n		&lt;tr&gt;\r\n			&lt;td style=&quot;width:300px&quot;&gt;\r\n				Furniture &amp;amp; Bulky Orders&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td&gt;\r\n				£60 Specialist Courier Service&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td style=&quot;width:300px&quot;&gt;\r\n				&amp;nbsp;&lt;/td&gt;\r\n		&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n		&lt;tr&gt;\r\n			&lt;td&gt;\r\n				&lt;p&gt;\r\n					&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n			&lt;/td&gt;\r\n		&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n	&lt;/tbody&gt;\r\n&lt;/table&gt;\r\n&lt;table border=&quot;0&quot; style=&quot;width: 1080px;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;tbody&gt;\r\n		&lt;tr&gt;\r\n			&lt;td&gt;\r\n				&lt;h2&gt;\r\n					Europe &amp;amp; The Rest Of The World&lt;/h2&gt;\r\n			&lt;/td&gt;\r\n		&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n		&lt;tr&gt;\r\n			&lt;td style=&quot;width: 300px;&quot;&gt;\r\n				Home Accessories &amp;amp; Fragrances etc.&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td&gt;\r\n				£25 - £60 Delivery Service*&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td style=&quot;width:300px&quot;&gt;\r\n				&amp;nbsp;&lt;/td&gt;\r\n		&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n		&lt;tr&gt;\r\n			&lt;td style=&quot;width:300px&quot;&gt;\r\n				Cards &amp;amp; Other Small Items&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td&gt;\r\n				£6.95 Royal Mail Delivery Service&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td style=&quot;width:300px&quot;&gt;\r\n				&amp;nbsp;&lt;/td&gt;\r\n		&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n		&lt;tr&gt;\r\n			&lt;td style=&quot;width:300px&quot;&gt;\r\n				Furniture &amp;amp; Bulky Orders&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td&gt;\r\n				Contact Us For A Quote&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td style=&quot;width:300px&quot;&gt;\r\n				&amp;nbsp;&lt;/td&gt;\r\n		&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n	&lt;/tbody&gt;\r\n&lt;/table&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:9px;&quot;&gt;*The shipping rate is dependant on the nature of your order and the location of the address it is to be delivered to. Please contact us if you have any questions.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;h2&gt;\r\n	Returns Infromation&lt;/h2&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	In the unlikely event that you are not satisfied with your purchase please return the item to us for a full refund or exchange within 7 days.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	We Refund or Exchange to the original payment method on any item that is returned in a resalable condition.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	If your item is faulty or damaged then please contact us immediately via email at hello@thepapillonshop.com.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	The cost of returning an item to us is your responsibility we will only refund the cost of delivery if it was our mistake or if the goods are damaged.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	A returns note is included in all deliveries please complete the form in full and return with your item.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	Refunds and exchanges can take up to 10 days to process from date of receipt, the returning item is your responsibility until it reaches us, we are not liable for lost items in transit.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	Please note that the Returns policy for online orders is not the same for items purchased instore, details of instore returns policy can be given by either calling 01273 720333 or via email at hello@thepapillonshop.com&lt;/p&gt;\r\n'),(34,1,'Privacy Policy','&lt;table border=&quot;0&quot; style=&quot;width: 1080px;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;tbody&gt;\r\n		&lt;tr&gt;\r\n			&lt;td&gt;\r\n				&lt;p&gt;\r\n					Papillon is committed to protecting your privacy. We will only use information given at the time of ordering or when making an enquiry by whatever means is collected lawfully and in accordance with the Data Protection Act 1998.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n					&lt;br /&gt;\r\n					We do not pass your personal information on to third parties.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n					&lt;br /&gt;\r\n					All transactions that you initiate with Papillon on this web site are confidential. Your name will not be added to any third party mailing lists.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n			&lt;/td&gt;\r\n		&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n		&lt;tr&gt;\r\n			&lt;td&gt;\r\n				&lt;h2&gt;\r\n					The Data Protection Act&lt;/h2&gt;\r\n				&lt;p&gt;\r\n					Under the terms of the Data Protection Act 1998, we have a duty to protect any information we collect from you. It will not be disclosed to any other organisation unless you give explicit permission, or there is a legal obligation to do so. We collect information about you for two main reasons:&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p&gt;\r\n					&lt;br /&gt;\r\n					&amp;nbsp;*&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; To process your online order.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n					&amp;nbsp;*&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; To provide you with the most efficient possible service.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n					&lt;br /&gt;\r\n					The information collected will be used to personally keep in touch and let you know of any offers, sales or promotions that Papillon are carrying out (if you have selected to receive these emails/newsletters).&lt;/p&gt;\r\n			&lt;/td&gt;\r\n		&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n		&lt;tr&gt;\r\n			&lt;td&gt;\r\n				&lt;h2&gt;\r\n					Right to request information&lt;/h2&gt;\r\n				&lt;p&gt;\r\n					You have a right to request a copy of any personal data held by Papillon at any time, in order to check its accuracy. If you wish to do this, please write (explaining that your interest is in personal data maintained by Papillon) to: Papillon, 8 Union Street, Brighton, East Sussex, BN1 1HA.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n			&lt;/td&gt;\r\n		&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n		&lt;tr&gt;\r\n			&lt;td&gt;\r\n				&lt;h2&gt;\r\n					Changes to this policy&lt;/h2&gt;\r\n				&lt;p&gt;\r\n					This privacy policy will change from time to time as we develop the range of services on the website. When this privacy policy changes, we will place an updated version on this page. Regularly reviewing this page ensures that you are always aware of what information we collect, how we use it and under what circumstances, if any, we will share it with other parties. You should always check the privacy policy before using this site, even if you have visited it in the past. This ensures that you will be aware of any changes. Changes to our privacy policy do not affect information we already hold about you. This statement was last updated on 4/6/10.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n			&lt;/td&gt;\r\n		&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n	&lt;/tbody&gt;\r\n&lt;/table&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n'),(35,1,'Terms &amp; Conditions','&lt;table border=&quot;0&quot; style=&quot;width: 1080px;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;tbody&gt;\r\n		&lt;tr&gt;\r\n			&lt;td&gt;\r\n				&lt;h2&gt;\r\n					Introduction&lt;/h2&gt;\r\n				&lt;p&gt;\r\n					The Supplier of the goods under your order is Papillon Retail Ltd 8 Union Street Brighton BN1 1HA. All Communication should be made at hello@thepapillonshop.com&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p&gt;\r\n					When you place an order we will require the following information:&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;ul&gt;\r\n					&lt;li&gt;\r\n						Your Name, Address, Telephone Number and a valid email address. You will also be required to give full details of a valid credit/debit card and Expiry date/&lt;/li&gt;\r\n				&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n				&lt;ul&gt;\r\n					&lt;li&gt;\r\n						Once your order is despatched the completion of the contract between Papillon and yourself is complete, should any problems arise prior to despatch we will contact you via email or phone.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n				&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n			&lt;/td&gt;\r\n		&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n		&lt;tr&gt;\r\n			&lt;td&gt;\r\n				&lt;h2&gt;\r\n					Refusal of Transaction&lt;/h2&gt;\r\n				&lt;p&gt;\r\n					We reserve the right to withdraw any product/products from this website at any time or, we may refuse to process any transaction for any reason or refuse service to anyone at any time at our sole discretion.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n					&lt;br /&gt;\r\n					We will not be liable to you or any third party by refusing to process a transaction or unwinding or suspending any transaction after processing has begun.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n			&lt;/td&gt;\r\n		&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n		&lt;tr&gt;\r\n			&lt;td&gt;\r\n				&lt;h2&gt;\r\n					Price and Payment&lt;/h2&gt;\r\n				&lt;p&gt;\r\n					The price for the goods is inclusive of VAT at the national standard rate. The current rates are correct at the time of entering onto our system.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n					&lt;br /&gt;\r\n					You confirm that the credit or debit card that is being used is yours. All credit/debit cardholders are subject to validation checks and authorisation by the card issuer. If the issuer of your payment card does not for any reason authorise payment to us, we will not be liable for any delay or non-delivery.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n					&lt;br /&gt;\r\n					You must pay in full for the goods (including any applicable delivery charges) at the time of placing your order.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n					&lt;br /&gt;\r\n					Ownership of the goods we supply to you will not pass until we have received all sums due and payable by you or in connection with the goods including where applicable delivery charges.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n			&lt;/td&gt;\r\n		&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n		&lt;tr&gt;\r\n			&lt;td&gt;\r\n				&lt;h2&gt;\r\n					Delivery&lt;/h2&gt;\r\n				&lt;p&gt;\r\n					At Papillon we aim to deliver an efficient service from when we first receive your order. All goods are sent via Interlink Express (next day service) who acts as our main Courier. (Please note that another courier may, at our discretion deliver certain items that are bulky such as furniture.)&lt;br /&gt;\r\n					&lt;br /&gt;\r\n					On occasion items may be lost or delayed in the post, due to a policy enforced by Royal Mail we must wait 14 days before we can resend new items or issue a refund.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n					&lt;br /&gt;\r\n					We will not resend any items until this time period elapses.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n					&lt;br /&gt;\r\n					If an item is sent to an address that you specified when you placed the order and it turns out to be incorrect then we are not liable if this item does not reach you.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n					&lt;br /&gt;\r\n					thepapillonshop.com is not liable for delays that are incurred via transit by Royal Mail or any other Courier it chooses to use.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n					Any orders placed over the weekend or during a Bank Holiday will be dealt with on the next working day.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n			&lt;/td&gt;\r\n		&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n		&lt;tr&gt;\r\n			&lt;td&gt;\r\n				&lt;h2&gt;\r\n					International Shipping&lt;/h2&gt;\r\n				&lt;p&gt;\r\n					If your delivery address is not within the United Kingdom, you may be subject to import duties and taxes, which are levied once a shipment reaches your country. Any such additional charges for customs clearance must be borne by you. You should note that customs policies vary widely from country to country; thepapillonshop.com advises each customer to contact their local customs office for further information.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n					&lt;br /&gt;\r\n					You should be aware that cross-border shipments are subject to opening and inspection by customs authorities.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n			&lt;/td&gt;\r\n		&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n		&lt;tr&gt;\r\n			&lt;td&gt;\r\n				&lt;h2&gt;\r\n					Enforcement of Terms and Conditions&lt;/h2&gt;\r\n				&lt;p&gt;\r\n					By accessing and using thepapillonshop.com website you agree that your access to and use of thepapillonshop.com website is subject to these terms and condition, as well as all applicable laws, as governed by and constructed in accordance with English Law. The parties to any such contract agree to submit to the exclusive jurisdiction of the courts of England and Wales.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n			&lt;/td&gt;\r\n		&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n		&lt;tr&gt;\r\n			&lt;td&gt;\r\n				&lt;h2&gt;\r\n					Returns&lt;/h2&gt;\r\n				&lt;p&gt;\r\n					In the unlikely event that you are not satisfied with your purchase please return the item to us for a full refund or exchange within 7 days.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n					&lt;br /&gt;\r\n					We Refund or Exchange to the original payment method on any item that is returned in a resalable condition.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n					&lt;br /&gt;\r\n					If your item is faulty or damaged then please contact us immediately via email at hello@thepapillonshop.com.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n					&lt;br /&gt;\r\n					The cost of returning an item to us is your responsibility we will only refund the cost of delivery if it was our mistake or if the goods are damaged.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n					&lt;br /&gt;\r\n					A returns note is included in all deliveries please complete the form in full and return with your item.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n					&lt;br /&gt;\r\n					Refunds and exchanges can take up to 10 days to process from date of receipt, the returning item is your responsibility until it reaches us, we are not liable for lost items in transit.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n					&lt;br /&gt;\r\n					Please note that Returns policy for instore purchases is not the same as our online policy.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n			&lt;/td&gt;\r\n		&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n	&lt;/tbody&gt;\r\n&lt;/table&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n'),(36,1,'Secure Shopping','&lt;h2&gt;\r\n	Why you can feel secure shopping with us&lt;/h2&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	When you shop with us, our secure server encrypts all of your personal information, including name, address and credit card information. We use SagePay which are an industry leader in secure internet transactions. SagePay are used by thousands of other UK businesses for transaction security.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;h2&gt;\r\n	Industry leading transaction security&lt;/h2&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	All transaction information passed between our website and the SagePay Payment System is encrypted using 128-bit SSL certificates. No cardholder information is ever passed unencrypted and all messages from SagePay are signed using MD5 hashing to prevent tampering. You can be completely secure in the knowledge that nothing passed to SagePay can be examined, used or modified by any third parties attempting to gain access to sensitive information.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;h2&gt;\r\n	Internationally recognised encryption and data storage&lt;/h2&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	Once on the SagePay system, all sensitive data is secured using the same internationally recognised 256-bit encryption standards used by, among others, the US Government. The encryption keys are held on state-of-the-art, tamper proof systems in the same family as those used to secure VeriSign\'s Global Root certificate, making them all but impossible to extract. The data they hold is extremely secure and they are regularly audited by the banks and banking authorities to ensure it remains so.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;h2&gt;\r\n	Private network links to banks&lt;/h2&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	SagePay has multiple private links into the banking network that are completely separate from the Internet and which do not cross any publicly accessible networks. Any cardholder information sent to the banks and any authorisation message coming back is secure and cannot be tampered with.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;h2&gt;\r\n	Employee access&lt;/h2&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	No individuals within our company or SagePay are able to decrypt transaction information or cardholder data. Their systems only allow access to our most senior staff and only in extenuating circumstances (such as investigations of Card Fraud by the Police). Your card information is secure even from their own employees because the systems never display the full card numbers, even on administration screens.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n'),(9,1,'Location','&lt;table align=&quot;top&quot; height=&quot;308&quot; width=&quot;100%&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;tbody&gt;\r\n		&lt;tr&gt;\r\n			&lt;td width=&quot;35%&quot;&gt;\r\n				&lt;div class=&quot;content clear-block&quot;&gt;\r\n					&lt;h1&gt;\r\n						Location&lt;/h1&gt;\r\n					&lt;p&gt;\r\n						Cadenhead\'s Whisky Shop &amp;amp; Tasting Room&lt;br /&gt;\r\n						26 Chiltern Street&lt;br /&gt;\r\n						London W1U 7QF&lt;/p&gt;\r\n					&lt;p&gt;\r\n						We will be happy to deal with any enquiries.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n						OPENING HOURS&lt;br /&gt;\r\n						Monday To Friday 10.30am-6.30pm&lt;br /&gt;\r\n						Saturday 10.30am-6.00pm&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;/div&gt;\r\n				&lt;p&gt;\r\n					&lt;iframe frameborder=&quot;0&quot; height=&quot;350&quot; marginheight=&quot;0&quot; marginwidth=&quot;0&quot; scrolling=&quot;no&quot; src=&quot;http://maps.google.co.uk/maps?f=q&amp;amp;hl=en&amp;amp;geocode=&amp;amp;q=26+Chiltern+Street,+London+W1U+7QF&amp;amp;sll=51.520627,-0.154624&amp;amp;sspn=0.012043,0.027595&amp;amp;g=26+Chiltern+Street,+London+W1U+7QF&amp;amp;ie=UTF8&amp;amp;s=AARTsJqAg_aH-uUznEuDMWawdaCQPECPBQ&amp;amp;ll=51.526421,-0.150375&amp;amp;spn=0.01869,0.036478&amp;amp;z=14&amp;amp;iwloc=addr&amp;amp;output=embed&quot; width=&quot;425&quot;&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n					&lt;small&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://maps.google.co.uk/maps?f=q&amp;amp;hl=en&amp;amp;geocode=&amp;amp;q=26+Chiltern+Street,+London+W1U+7QF&amp;amp;sll=51.520627,-0.154624&amp;amp;sspn=0.012043,0.027595&amp;amp;g=26+Chiltern+Street,+London+W1U+7QF&amp;amp;ie=UTF8&amp;amp;ll=51.526421,-0.150375&amp;amp;spn=0.01869,0.036478&amp;amp;z=14&amp;amp;iwloc=addr&amp;amp;source=embed&quot; style=&quot;color:#0000FF;text-align:left&quot;&gt;View Larger Map&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/small&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n			&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td valign=&quot;top&quot; width=&quot;45%&quot;&gt;\r\n				&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;http://boundless-cart.local/image/data/cadenheads/Location_cadenheads.png&quot; style=&quot;width: 382px; height: 240px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;\r\n		&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n	&lt;/tbody&gt;\r\n&lt;/table&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n'),(7,1,'Whisky Tasting','&lt;table align=&quot;top&quot; height=&quot;308&quot; width=&quot;100%&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;tbody&gt;\r\n		&lt;tr&gt;\r\n			&lt;td width=&quot;70%&quot;&gt;\r\n				&lt;div class=&quot;content clear-block&quot;&gt;\r\n					&lt;div class=&quot;image-attach-body&quot; style=&quot;width: 300px&quot;&gt;\r\n						&lt;h1&gt;\r\n							Whisky Tasting&lt;/h1&gt;\r\n					&lt;/div&gt;\r\n					&lt;p&gt;\r\n						&lt;strong&gt;Trip Around Scotland&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n						At our &lt;a href=&quot;http://whisky.local/index.php?route=information/information&amp;amp;information_id=9&quot;&gt;London Tasting Room&lt;/a&gt;, we hold regular Whisky Tastings,&lt;/p&gt;\r\n					&lt;p&gt;\r\n						each tasting is limited to 12 people and demand is usually high.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n					&lt;div class=&quot;image-attach-body&quot; style=&quot;width: 300px&quot;&gt;\r\n						&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n					&lt;p&gt;\r\n						&lt;strong&gt;All of our Whisky tastings feature:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n					&lt;ul&gt;\r\n						&lt;li&gt;\r\n							Six whiskies from across the regions of Scotland&lt;/li&gt;\r\n						&lt;li&gt;\r\n							Different types of cask maturation&lt;/li&gt;\r\n						&lt;li&gt;\r\n							A brief history of whisky and how it is made&lt;/li&gt;\r\n						&lt;li&gt;\r\n							Information on each distillery included in the tasting&lt;/li&gt;\r\n						&lt;li&gt;\r\n							&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.whiskytastingroom.com/canapes-0&quot;&gt;Canapes&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n					&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n					&lt;p&gt;\r\n						All in the intimate and informal setting of our dedicated Tasting Room.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n						The cost per person is £28.50&lt;/p&gt;\r\n					&lt;p&gt;\r\n						You can &lt;a href=&quot;http://whisky.local/index.php?route=information/event/events&amp;amp;event_id=2&quot;&gt;view our calendar&lt;/a&gt; if you would like to to find out when we are holding tastings or &lt;a href=&quot;http://whisky.local/index.php?route=information/contact&quot;&gt;contact us&lt;/a&gt; for further information.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n					&lt;p&gt;\r\n						&lt;strong&gt;Whisky Tasting Experience&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n						&lt;em&gt;A &lt;a href=&quot;http://whisky.local/index.php?route=information/information&amp;amp;information_id=25&quot;&gt;Whisky Tasting Experience&lt;/a&gt; can be arranged for groups between 1 to 5 people, please &lt;a href=&quot;http://whisky.local/index.php?route=information/contact&quot;&gt;contact us&lt;/a&gt; for further information or to book. &lt;strong&gt;Whisky Tasting Experiences&lt;/strong&gt; can be booked from Monday to Saturday, the first appointment at 11:00 and the last at 17:00&lt;/em&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n						The cost per person is £18.50&lt;/p&gt;\r\n					&lt;p&gt;\r\n						&lt;strong&gt;Private Group Tastings&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n						&lt;em&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://whisky.local/index.php?route=information/information&amp;amp;information_id=26&quot;&gt;Private Group Tastings&lt;/a&gt; can be arranged on Tuesdays, Wednesdays, Thursdays and Saturdays for groups of 6 to 15 people, please &lt;a href=&quot;http://whisky.local/index.php?route=information/contact&quot;&gt;contact us&lt;/a&gt; for further information or to book.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n					&lt;p&gt;\r\n						&lt;strong&gt;Off Site Whisky Tasting&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n						&lt;em&gt;If you have a larger group then 15 people we can also arrange for tastings at other locations. For instance, local restaurants like &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.hardys-w1.com/index.php&quot;&gt;Hardy\'s&lt;/a&gt; can accommodate larger groups. Please &lt;a href=&quot;http://whisky.local/index.php?route=information/contact&quot;&gt;contact us&lt;/a&gt; for further information or to book.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n					&lt;p&gt;\r\n						&lt;strong&gt;Stay Informed&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n						&lt;em&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://whisky.local/index.php?route=information/contact&quot;&gt;Contact us&lt;/a&gt; if you would like us to keep you informed of Whisky Tastings as we arrange them and we will add you to our mailing list.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;/div&gt;\r\n			&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td valign=&quot;top&quot; width=&quot;30%&quot;&gt;\r\n				&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;http://boundless-cart.local/image/data/cadenheads/whisky tasting_cadenheads.png&quot; style=&quot;width: 246px; height: 575px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;\r\n		&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n	&lt;/tbody&gt;\r\n&lt;/table&gt;\r\n'),(48,1,'Product Care','&lt;div class=&quot;text-info&quot; id=&quot;right&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;div class=&quot;copy&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;p&gt;\r\n			&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n		&lt;p&gt;\r\n			Our waterproof socks and gloves use patented technology, ensuring the ultimate in waterproof and breathable protection for the feet and hands.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n		&lt;p&gt;\r\n			Great in the cold and wet, the waterproof technology keeps you warm and dry. Even when it’s warm, sweat is pulled away from the body and leaves through the highly breathable membrane.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n		&lt;p&gt;\r\n			As a result SealSkinz products ensure your feet, hands and head always remain totally dry. They also reduce the chance of blisters on your feet as the three-layer technology helps to prevent your foot being rubbed against your shoe.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n		&lt;p&gt;\r\n			SealSkinz exceptional technology uses a unique seamless three layer construction – an outer, a waterproof, highly breathable membrane and an inner lining.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n		&lt;div class=&quot;info-technology&quot;&gt;\r\n			&lt;h3&gt;\r\n				How They Work&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n			&lt;div class=&quot;how-they-work first&quot;&gt;\r\n				&lt;h3&gt;\r\n					Inner Layer&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n				&lt;p&gt;\r\n					The inner lining has been specially developed to actively wick moisture away from the skin to increase comfort and warmth and reduce the chance of blisters. It is made from either Coolmax or Merino wool.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n			&lt;/div&gt;\r\n			&lt;div class=&quot;how-they-work middle&quot;&gt;\r\n				&lt;h3&gt;\r\n					Middle Layer&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n				&lt;p&gt;\r\n					The waterproof breathable membrane is inserted using patented technology and allows perspiration, as water vapour to escape whilst preventing water coming in. The membrane typically has a breathability of greater than 65% WVP, making the socks and gloves completely waterproof, highly breathable and windproof.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n			&lt;/div&gt;\r\n			&lt;div class=&quot;how-they-work last&quot;&gt;\r\n				&lt;h3&gt;\r\n					Outer Layer&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n				&lt;p&gt;\r\n					The outer layer is designed for extra durability and abrasion resistance with stretch to fit properties. It is tough and durable designed to stand up to all weather conditions.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n			&lt;/div&gt;\r\n		&lt;/div&gt;\r\n		&lt;img src=&quot;http://www.sealskinz.com/includes/templates/sealskinz/images/technology/technologies-how-they-work.jpg&quot; /&gt; &lt;a name=&quot;product-care&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;\r\n		&lt;h2 style=&quot;color:#000;font-size:20px;padding-left:20px;&quot;&gt;\r\n			Product Care Instructions&lt;/h2&gt;\r\n		&lt;p&gt;\r\n			SealSkinz products can be machine washed up to 40&lt;sup&gt;o&lt;/sup&gt;C and some can be tumble dried. It is advised that you do not iron or dry out on a radiator or other direct heat source.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n		&lt;img src=&quot;http://www.sealskinz.com/includes/templates/sealskinz/images/technology/technologies-care-instructions.gif&quot; /&gt;\r\n		&lt;p&gt;\r\n			These specific instructions relate to our socks, Ultra Grip and Ultra Tough gloves. For all other products please refer to their individual wash care labels.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n'),(49,1,'Testimonials','&lt;p&gt;\r\n	&amp